747
01:05:53,589 --> 01:05:54,689
Jin Woo.

748
01:05:56,390 --> 01:05:57,589
Ayo bicara.

749
01:05:58,990 --> 01:06:00,930
Kasus kita belakangan ini

750
01:06:01,300 --> 01:06:02,729
